This Mobile App was built using React Native with the help of Expo Client on iOS device/simulator. You can equally run it on your Android device

HOW TO USE APP
****************** Add Task ******************
When you Click on Add Task a Modal will be displayed requesting you to input your task
After Your task has been inputed in the text input you then click on Add
Modal will be closed and your inputed text will be displayed
You can go through the process again to add more tasks and they will all be displayed for you

****************** Delete Task ******************
To Delete a task you will need to go to the tasks display and long press to delete task of your choice

****************** Cancel/Close Modal ******************
When you Click on Add Task a Modal will be displayed requesting you to input your task
If you have no need of adding a task you can click on the Cancel button which will close the modal automatically.
